InspirePlayed
Bukkit Plugin

This is my first plugin for my Bukkit Minecraft Server!
This plugin (I hope) will be able to track the playtime of users on my server.

Planned Features (in order):
-implement /played basic feature
-implement /played <player> to check other playtimes
-Send back original capitalization of player's name
-use MySQL
-add configurable file to change colours and prefix
-detect afk players
-promote users to next rank after certain amount of time

Changelog:
May 23, 2011
0.2 - Player's name not case-sensitive anymore, saves data file on player logout and on /played
May 21, 2011
0.1 - Initial